Interface Log

All Superinterfaces:
org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
All Known Implementing Classes:
Log_$logger
@MessageLogger(projectCode="ISPN") @ValidIdRange(min=12001, max=13000) public interface Log extends org.jboss.logging.BasicLogger
Log abstraction for the REST server module. For this module, message ids ranging from 12001 to 13000 inclusively have been reserved.
Since:
5.0
Author:
Galder Zamarre√±o
